file.name: produces_consumes_test.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
info:
  version: 1.0.0
  title: Test spec for OpenAPI3RouterBuilderTest consumes and produces tests
  license:
    name: Apache 2.0 License
paths:
  /consumesTest:
    post:
      operationId: consumesTest
      requestBody:
        required: true
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              type: object
              required:
                - name
              properties:
                name:
                  type: string
          application/x-www-form-urlencoded:
            schema:
              type: object
              required:
                - name
              properties:
                name:
                  type: string
      responses:
        default:
          description: ok
  /producesTest:
    get:
      operationId: producesTest
      parameters:
        - name: fail
          in: query
          required: false
          schema:
            type: boolean
            default: false
      responses:
        default:
          description: ok
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: object
                required:
                  - name
                properties:
                  name:
                    type: string
        500:
          description: Error
          content:
            text/plain:
              schema:
                type: string
components: {}

Error: notImplemented: path "/producesTest": get: responses: 500: contents: unsupported content types: [text/plain]
